    "In contrast, it successfully detects out-of-distribution constructs.",
    "7 Effects of WANDA Pruning on Linear Models with Correlated Input Features",
    "In this section, we empirically validate that WANDA pruning significantly reduces test loss in Ordinary Least Squares (OLS) Regression models when the input features are correlated.",
    "This scenario is relevant in the context of large language models because natural language follows many structural patterns, such as power law, and the representations are not independent across different dimensions.",
    "Understanding the regularizing effects of WANDA pruning for a linear model can offer valuable insights for understanding its effects on more complex models."
